Calls `gnus-sync-lesync-set-prop'.
For the 'rev PROP, uses '_rev against the document."
  (gnus-sync-lesync-set-prop
   prop key (cdr (assq (if (eq prop 'rev) '_rev prop)
                       (gnus-sync-lesync-GET url nil)))))

